 | |__| (_) | | | | |_| |  | | |_) / ___ \\ | |
  \\____\\___/|_| |_|\\__|_|  |_|_.__/_/   \\_\\___|

  [dim]AI Agent for Open Source Contributions v{__version__}[/dim]
[/bold cyan]"""
